Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================MAIN========================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入乔康达公爵城堡的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽想从其内部推翻他们的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之外的人和名字却接二连三地冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红法师雷藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上连暗杀者祖玛和乔康达都出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来给我说明一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Judgment 甦醒的白银
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手都不是泛泛之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 尽是些难对付的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也只能拼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只好鸡蛋碰石头了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可别那么容易挂掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也得让我兴奋起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶 你好歹也算是这里的领主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖退到观众席上去观摩如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 我没有旁观战斗的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是为我而造的斗技场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我享受打倒猎物的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真有雅兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有折磨猎物的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能逃过我的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 大婶 还是别来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长这类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是再囉囉嗦嗦疏忽大意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是受伤就能了事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧塞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你牵制那两个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是契约的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰路 阿梅莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}（你圣斗士啊…）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的招数对我没用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 被看穿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人倒是都会以为已识破的手法对手不会再用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难啃的骨头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然 人说连魔王也拒不食我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强吃下去 也只会弄坏肚子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我塔夫拉西亚 曾经封印了过去的魔导都市赛拉格的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你要打破这禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有力量的人 连救助也得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算靠那力量拯救塔夫拉西亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该记得 那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是突如其来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击塔夫拉西亚的疫病 很快就蔓延了开去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时没有治疗这疫病的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样下去 说不定塔夫拉西亚真的会灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红法师雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是我也无法治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能让人们在找到治疗法之前进入沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们貌似也已染上了这疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你们暂时的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要有人保护这个沉眠的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也需要有人去寻求疾病治疗法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是因那个壶而变成这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这应该是为了保护塔夫拉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是为了打破禁忌 进行复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是有必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护塔夫拉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使用那力量夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不也是只会玷污塔夫拉西亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞到了 撞到腰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东游西晃的竟然走到这种地方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这里是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有趣的对战牌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果会如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地击冲雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵王结魔弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很卑鄙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Shadow Snap{\r}\N影缚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明球…才怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是火焰球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即场用地精道之类的 潜入地下了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收起你的剑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没兴趣砍女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有一套的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的剑技 有资格当我的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈 丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈 丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你适合当我的第五个丈夫 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要当我的丈夫 那你就是公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想品尝一下贵族的生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 顺便问一下之前的四个怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他们都是不错的剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都已在这斗技场命丧黄泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别 别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事我心领就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚灵障界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在意同伴的安危吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风结咒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平主义者之拳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩灵裂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这黑暗果然会吸收咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没有光之剑 你就无法可想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倾听你同伴的惨叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅莉亚 杰路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 这里就是制造那魔导战车的研究所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟是个这么煞风景的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 这不是那腹语术人偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记自我介绍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鲁比那加尔德王国特别搜查官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监察官维瑟·弗雷昂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实传闻这领内局势不稳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这公爵领地从以前起就恶评不断嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对领民的暴政 伪造货币 黑市买卖人口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至倒卖送往邻国的救援物资
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援物资
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据闻从诸国收集了救援物资准备送往疫病蔓延的邻国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知不觉就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而因那邻国本身突然间消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就不了了之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说没有证据 我也不敢断言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你的腹语术真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是腹语术的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恨就恨莉娜·因巴斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子对莉娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.13,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悪梦の王のひと欠片よ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.57,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空の戒め解き放たれし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.31,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氷れる黒き虚无の刃よ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:21.19,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我が力、我が身となりて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.78,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ともに滅びの道を歩まん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:27.91,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神々の魂すらも打ち砕き
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.82,jpww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇を以って闇を切り裂け
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.13,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噩梦之王的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.57,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放天空之戒令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.31,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冻的黑色虚无之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:21.19,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作吾力及吾身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.78,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同走向毁灭之程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:27.91,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击溃众神之魂魄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.82,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以暗破暗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:36.59,ww,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs24}Laguna Blade\N{\r}神灭斩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这咒文 持续时间依然很短
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧塞尔 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是契约的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能撑到这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然以暗噬暗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会的咒语还真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借用金色魔王力量的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝招吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我调查你所得的资料里也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说调查我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据闻一流的暗杀者 会详细分析目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为身为暗杀者才知道你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为知道你 我才会选择暗杀者这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说为了夺我性命 你才会当暗杀者？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手应该是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 莉娜·因巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该没空担心别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟扔掉了对剑士来说比命还重要的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你始终也不过如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打不中也没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一把打不中的话那两把如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿双剑的话 高里消耗的体力会大很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 也无法配合他俩的速度打出咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好会打中高里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用黑暗咒语 可不是你的专利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Dark Mist{\r}\N黑雾炎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边是光之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 在黑暗中把剑换手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正经打找不到你的破绽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炎矢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚灵障界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃 逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说还会来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖的执念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做了什么让他这么恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯 你这是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想背叛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从诸国收集而来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送往塔夫拉西亚的救援物资哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 听信了那男人的胡话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是胡话由我们决定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时至今日再狡辩也没用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援物资的确有集中起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而也的确没被送到塔夫拉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算救援物资送到 那疫病也不会平息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也是白费的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也许的确如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若那些救援物资有送到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔夫拉西亚的人民会获得多大的鼓励呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也没有践踏这份心意的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类可是意外地没那么坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的意思是我不是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 大婶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那边总算搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这边也够凄惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来这大婶就是罪魁祸首啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然被这种家伙给骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我面前这么做会给我添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹让她接受正式的制裁也是我的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为塞伦代表 也希望她接受鲁比那加尔德王国公正的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说公正的制裁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为那种东西能解我塔夫拉西亚之苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去品尝比地底还要深沉的黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是沙那法之铠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的手感原来是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯 你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位小心点好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔康达夫人所穿着的是完全的沙那法之铠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说完全的沙那法之铠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 跟迪克利斯先生所穿着的不完全的沙那法之铠不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忠实再现了异界默示录抄本内容的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎会 造出那种东西的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之剑在鸣动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 这不是完美的沙那法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那的确是完美的沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道你以为牠是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是魔兽沙那法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================ED========================
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}終わりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:54.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这不是终点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}{\pos(861,445)}{\fscx80\fs16}あめ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}晴れ渡る空から 落ちるとおり涙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:04.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}晴朗的空中落下雨泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:10.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}流れてゆく雲に 追いつけなくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:10.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}漂浮的流云无从追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:16.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}旅立ちの先には 新しい出会い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:16.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}旅途前方是新的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:22.82,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}でも流されてるようで 落ち着かなくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:22.82,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}但随波逐流的感觉令人不安
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.54,0:22:29.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}それでも この瞬間に
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.54,0:22:29.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}即便如此 这一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:36.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}全てが　終わる　訳じゃない そうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:36.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}并非一切都已结束 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:41.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あきれる程 悩み抜いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:41.92,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}摆脱那些琐碎的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:47.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}出ない答え 今はいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:47.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}未知的答案 现在已不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:53.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ほら本当は　あきらめていない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:53.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}看吧 其实你并没放弃
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.27,0:22:57.05,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}まだまだ行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.27,0:22:57.05,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}还能继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:59.76,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}終わりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:59.76,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}这不是终点
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.89,0:23:03.16,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一緒に行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.89,0:23:03.16,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}与我同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}覚悟決めてね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========================NEXT========================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的魔兽沙那法终于复活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你复活这种东西到底想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.25,0:23:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普库塔 你一个人要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slayers Revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep out 悄悄靠近的魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看的话我可要发飙咯！
